<h2 id="what-else-is-possible">What Else is Possible?</h2>

<p>After getting pretty good with all this, I wonder what other options there are. Raspberry Pi SBCs now come with significant amounts of RAM and the Raspbian operating system is based on Debian. As a matter of fact, there are even Ubuntu and Debian distributions available for the Raspberry Pi.</p>

